    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) In Dei nomine amen. Millesimo centesimo quarto, indictione duodecima,
                        die dominico qui fuit sextus exeunte aprelis. Ego <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissa</rs>
                        <persName
                            key="#Countess #childOf #grandchildOf #Churches #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Specialized_workers #Forests #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#people/125">Matilda</persName>, Dei gratia si quid sum, <rs
                            key="#childOf">filia</rs> quondam <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #parentOf" ref="#people/1">Bonifatii</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionis</rs> tibi <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/2189">Alberico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Churches #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Specialized_workers #Forests #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Districtio"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti in Larione</orgName>
                        nomine et vice eiusdem monasterii cui preesse videris, quicquid pater et <rs
                            key="#grandparentOf">avus</rs> meus <persName key="#grandparentOf"
                            ref="#people/2122">Tedaldus</persName> dederunt predicto monasterio
                        Sancti Benedicti in <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/2959">Casalavone</placeName>, videlicet <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2074">Sancti
                            Michaelis</orgName> de <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/2936"
                            >Cotornione</placeName>, et alias posessiones silicet <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casamenta</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes">agros</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">roncos de bosco</rs> Casalavone, quod <rs
                            key="#Forests">nemus</rs> est <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >iuris mei</rs>; et <rs key="#Specialized_workers">piscatores</rs> in
                            <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs> illius terre, duos
                        aut tres et plus secundum voluntatem nuntii tui, per totum in integrum
                        concedo et confirmo in perpetuum, ut tu supradictus abbas et tui successores
                        habeas et teneas sine mea et heredum meorum contradictione. Et tibi hanc
                        potestatem concedo et tuis successoribus, pro anima mea et parentum meorum
                        ut nuncii tui, qui pro tempore fuerunt ibi, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">de predicto bosco et aliis
                            nemoribus illius terre roncare et boscare et pavolare et uti et
                            frui</rs> debeant, sine molestia et contradictione nostra et nostrorum
                        ut supra legitur; quam potestatem antecessores mei tuis antecessoribus
                        dederunt. Insuper quicquid monasterium tuum Sancti Benedicti in illa terra
                        mea aquirere vel lucrari poterit, cum mea licencia et heredum meorum facere
                        debeat; eo modo ut predictum monasterium Santi Benedicti habeat et teneat
                        omnia predicta cum omni honore et <rs key="#Districtio">districtu et
                            bannis</rs>. Actum est hoc in <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/145">Nogarie</placeName> feliciter,
                        presente <persName key="#Bishops #Witness" ref="#people/2190"
                            >Ugone</persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/275" key="#Bishops">Mantue</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs>. Huius re <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count #Witness" ref="#people/2196">Wido Guarra</persName>,
                        comes <persName key="#Count #Witness" ref="#people/2197">Albertus</persName>
                        filius <persName><name ref="Boso">Bosonis</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/3500">Arduinus</persName>, <persName
                            ref="#people/3780" key="#Witness">Gerardus</persName> filius
                                <persName><name ref="Boso">Bosonis</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/2199">Ugo</persName> filius <persName
                            ref="#people/3510">Manfredi</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/2193">Sasso</persName> et <persName ref="#people/2198"
                            >Rainerius</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2468"
                            >Bibianello</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/3516"
                            >Lanfrancus</persName> et <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/3517"
                            >Opizo</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2414">Gonzaga</placeName>
                        et alii plures. (S.) Ego <persName key="#Judge #Notary #Writer"
                            ref="#people/3539">Ubaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> hoc <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et dedi. </ab>
